P.S....a great tip....my cousin "hates" garlic so i use a microplane...hates the idea of big chunks of it but actually loves the taste.....plus, my mothet buys jalapeno chilis in bulk from our produce store....she then grinds it up in a food processor, seeds and all, keeps it in a tupperware container, so I just add spoonfuls of it when needed...you can freeze it too.....it sounds weird but it is so convenient and great and yummy. Just a tip!! Happy cooking!

