This rich lasagna is very simple, although somewhat time-consuming to make. It feeds well over 8 people (unless they play pro football) and needs to be baked in a *deep* 13x9" pan. Use the spiciest Italian sausage you can find. The cheeses will blunt the spice a little. It also reheats very well.

